scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Pieces included: 1 Score, 1 CD, 1 submission letter, 1 biographical note. Notes: The CD and a duplicate of the score were in a manila envelope on which was written "Kentucky New Music Festival, Sop/Mz-sop submissions." Note on envelope AW1.1 .05..
